Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And I go to Page 12 of Head MRI
Then 'Diagnosis' tab is enabled and preselected
And 'Procedure/course' tab is enabled
And 'Diagnosis' dropdown is enabled

When I select 'Multiple sclerosis' from 'Diagnosis' dropdown
Then 'Add classification' button is enabled
And 'Periventricular' checkbox is enabled
And 'Cortical' checkbox is enabled
And 'Juxtacortical' checkbox is enabled
And 'Infratentorial' checkbox is enabled
And 'Spinal' checkbox is enabled
And 'Optic neuritis' checkbox is enabled
And 'Differential diagnosis' dropdown is enabled

When I select 'Periventricular' checkbox
Then 'Periventricular' checkbox is selected
And 'Periventricular' input field is enabled
When I enter 1 in 'Periventricular' input field
Then the value is accepted
When I enter 99 in 'Periventricular' input field
Then the value is accepted

When I select 'Cortical' checkbox
Then 'Cortical' checkbox is selected
And 'Cortical' input field is enabled
When I enter 1 in 'Cortical' input field
Then the value is accepted
When I enter 99 in 'Cortical' input field
Then the value is accepted

When I select 'Juxtacortical' checkbox
Then 'Juxtacortical' checkbox is selected
And 'Juxtacortical' input field is enabled
When I enter 1 in 'Juxtacortical' input field
Then the value is accepted
When I enter 99 in 'Juxtacortical' input field
Then the value is accepted

When I select 'Infratentorial' checkbox
Then 'Infratentorial' checkbox is selected
And 'Infratentorial' input field is enabled
When I enter 1 in 'Infratentorial' input field
Then the value is accepted
When I enter 99 in 'Infratentorial' input field
Then the value is accepted

When I select 'Spinal' checkbox
Then 'Spinal' checkbox is selected
And 'Spinal' input field is enabled
When I enter 1 in 'Spinal' input field
Then the value is accepted
When I enter 99 in 'Spinal' input field
Then the value is accepted

When I select 'Optic neuritis' checkbox
Then 'Optic neuritis' checkbox is selected
And 'Right' checkbox is enabled
And 'Right' checkbox is enabled
When I select 'Right' checkbox
And I select 'Left' checkbox
Then 'Right' checkbox is selected
And 'Left' checkbox is selected

When I select 'Fungal infection' from 'Differential diagnosis' dropdown
Then 'Fungal infection' is selected
